{"tid":1291092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有關連儂牆。","createTime":"2019-07-06T17:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:31:23.000Z","uid":37250,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"004322ab169ac2187df1dfdf802c539441ad0c1c","tid":1291092,"uid":37250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"眼見好多地區都開始有連儂牆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遍地開花 的確係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我見到好似黃大仙個連儂牆  好似冇瓦遮頭<br />\n我擔心一落雨就會整到濕晒同埋甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話甩咗可以再貼過上去 但始終都係人地嘅心意<br />\n所以之後嘅連儂牆 大家會唔會考慮下個地方 <br />\n起碼有瓦遮頭 唔使日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算會甩都唔會咁快甩<br />\n純粹個人意見"},{"pid":"6b9e5fbce26a91b246d8e4c8eac2b56ae65f68b8","tid":1291092,"uid":37250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:30:05.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"6abedbd6465f8d5bd1c9af7b93021d802d793a86","tid":1291092,"uid":37250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"44d272b0b843af5a88075df2ee163acfafbc2612","tid":1291092,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7twnFnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7twnFnB.jpg&h=df2571ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3Kkr2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3Kkr2C.jpg&h=b6c70bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTXidHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTXidHD.jpg&h=a6d55b00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc86f0f36a95aabf9c7ae43b335c2609f36d1e3e","tid":1291092,"uid":37250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"e79ec50cabc51b69866921c9c6ab